Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:01:59.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:06.01,Titles,,0,0,0,,Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that... Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:10.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:11.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Onashia...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to Onashia, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:18.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:24.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is where you decided to be, isn't it, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun has made her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,She has chosen her path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yun will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:59.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think... perhaps I should have come here earlier with my friends from Rubor. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's enter together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:13.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, you've been through a lot, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, did you do everything you wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to offer a prayer with one of the ancient Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I wanted to {\i1}fly{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:36.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to sit in the captain's chair of the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}, just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:51.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel as though... I do not truly know everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:59.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,None of us really know anything about one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,But in order to understand, we must fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,While we scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even while we are so afraid that our hearts leap from our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,We hold ourselves together and fall... endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,And sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we get so afraid of the fall that we cling to something along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:33.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... we have to let go, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:37.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be there waiting, somewhere in that abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses of Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that title is no longer suitable for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,But yes, they should be returning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to learning what the priestesses of Chor Tempest have chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm looking forward to that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,And what about those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that they will end up being our final responsibility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Back there... Yun was supporting us, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was almost like being in a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of our feelings, all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, we're—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:28.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does my heart hurt so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know the answer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:57.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does my heart hurt like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because you are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is... love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. That is love, Aaeru. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I you, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria... she was strong, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was. She was a strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:10.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,A rendezvous with a Plumbish priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a scandalous affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,This will probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:21.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the last duty I can perform for the sibyllae of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:26.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope that Tempus Spatium will forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:32.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still remember Sibylla Neviril's words during the hearing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:40.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to lay blame for these days of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:44.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It has been painful and heartbreaking, and perhaps this is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:47.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It may even be the will of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,But right now, I don't care what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't care about "the will of God."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:59.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just have one question I'd like to ask you all:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,In spite of that... am I still a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:23.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think you might still be a sibylla, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The others are waiting on the observation deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:40.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You guys can come join us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, and thank you, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Paraietta. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you... dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The soldiers are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:46.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are still two priestesses who have not yet entered the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:57.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,When do they plan to head for the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,How was the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people there were in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw lots of smiling faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Were you bored, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I did some Maaju by myself, and drank some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You guys didn't change much, eh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to be female.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm female too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Male?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose male too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:36.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,They will go as soon as they feel they are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:51.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a very important condition in the peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:58.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but there is no mention of any time limit for that clause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason I did not choose Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:15.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because I didn't want to betray you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:20.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was simply an excuse to protect my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was silly of me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wanting to remain a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, how childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I was chosen as a pair to complete the Emerald Ri Maajon."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I am a tool to them."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:54.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I convinced myself that Amuria and Aaeru chose me for those reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:01.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} was the one who was attracted to their unwavering pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've realized that they are far purer than I{** me}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:12.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,They aren't afraid of getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:15.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly it, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've decided to live true to my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you stop living by forcing your feelings upon others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,it feels as though you're standing in another, larger world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I was always waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I came to believe that everything was the fault of the one I cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't keep on living like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:41.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to feel truly loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to be female.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,We shall make arrangements for them to be taken to the Spring by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our soldiers will accompany them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose female.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:18.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too. I chose to be female.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea. Please, wait here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! Neviril and Aaeru mustn't go to the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're our...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:23.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our present is on their shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:30.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, is this really part of the treaty that Simulacrum signed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will never let them be taken to the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:43.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The eternal now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see you, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:04.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to touch you, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't, Alti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:15.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that title belongs to me any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:23.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have asked for permission to give our sibyllae a final farewell before they go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:29.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the best that the captain of the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} was able to do for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's an unusually barbaric act, coming from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:13.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:20.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe. Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is goodbye, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You two can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:06.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura. Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:08.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:11.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:12.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:14.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again... someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Eternal Priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:21.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:26.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the story of what happened to the girls thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:30.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on the final Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:33.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their Portrait.
